  m_text: "CHARACTER CREDITS\r\n\r\nPlayer Character:\r\nBase/body assets and related
    LPC character parts by contributors including\r\nbluecarrot16, JaidynReiman,
    Benjamin K. Smith (BenCreating), Evert,\r\nEliza Wyatt (ElizaWy), TheraHedwig,
    MuffinElZangano, Durrani,\r\nJohannes Sj\xF6lund (wulax), and Stephen Challener
    (Redshrike).\r\n\r\nAdditional player parts also credit contributors such as\r\nFabzy,
    Matthew Krohn (makrohn), Michael Whitlock (bigbeargames),\r\nNila122, and pennomi
    / laetissima.\r\n\r\nEnemy Characters:\r\nEnemy assets include work by contributors
    such as\r\nbluecarrot16, JaidynReiman, Stephen Challener (Redshrike),\r\nWilliam.Thomsponj,
    ElizaWy, Johannes Sj\xF6lund (wulax),\r\nMichael Whitlock (bigbeargames), and
    others.\r\n\r\nAsset Sources:\r\nOpenGameArt LPC / Liberated Pixel Cup assets
    and expansions\r\n\r\nLicenses used in these assets may include:\r\nOGA-BY 3.0\r\nCC-BY-SA
    3.0\r\nCC-BY 3.0 / 4.0\r\nGPL 2.0 / 3.0\r\nCC0"
